mande avec un carnet d'heures prépayé.</div><a id="link_button-71-27" class="ct-link-button" href="/it-maintenance/maintenance-nettime/" target="_self"  >Plus d'info sur NetTime</a></div></div><div id="div_block-78-27" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="div_block-79-27" class="ct-div-block atomic-iconblock-15-wrapper" ><div id="text_block-80-27" class="ct-text-block" >Forfait</div><h3 id="headline-81-27" class="ct-headline">NetGlobal</h3><div id="div_block-82-27" class="ct-div-block oxel_horizontal_divider" ><div id="code_block-83-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div><div id="code_block-84-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div></div><div id="text_block-85-27" class="ct-text-block atomic-iconblock-15-text" >Maintenance préventive et curative forfaitaire&nbsp;Raccordement au système de monitoring et d'alertes.</div><a id="link_button-86-27" class="ct-link-button" href="/it-maintenance/netglobalmaintenance/" target="_self"  >Plus d'info sur NetGlobal</a></div></div><div id="div_block-87-27" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="div_block-88-27" class="ct-div-block atomic-iconblock-15-wrapper" ><div id="text_block-89-27" class="ct-text-block" >Forfait</div><h3 id="headline-90-27" class="ct-headline">NetPRO</h3><div id="div_block-91-27" class="ct-div-block oxel_horizontal_divider" ><div id="code_block-92-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div><div id="code_block-93-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div></div><div id="text_block-94-27" class="ct-text-block atomic-iconblock-15-text" >Forfait annuel tout inclus(maintenance, monitoring et nouvelles mise en service)</div><a id="link_button-95-27" class="ct-link-button" href="/it-maintenance/netpro-maintenance/" target="_self"  >Plus d'info sur NetPRO</a></div></div></div></div></section><link rel='stylesheet' id='oxygen-unslider-css'  href='https://evok.com/wp-content/plugins/oxygen/component-framework/vendor/unslider/unslider.css' type='text/css' media='all'/><div id="slider-105-27" class="ct-slider ct_unique_slider_7531" ><div class="oxygen-unslider-container"><ul><li><div id="slide-106-27" class="ct-slide" ><div id="new_columns-130-27" class="ct-new-columns" ><div id="div_block-132-27" class="ct-div-block" ><img  id="image-171-27" alt="" src="https://evok.com/media/illustrations_svg-1.svg.png" class="ct-image"/></div><div id="div_block-24-27" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="div_block-574-27" class="ct-div-block" ><img  id="image-158-27" alt="" src="https://evok.com/media/banner.png" class="ct-image"/><h4 id="headline-13-27" class="ct-headline">All-Flash Storage, Infrastructure convergée, NAS, Archivage, Object&nbsp;Storage</h4><div id="text_block-15-27" class="ct-text-block" >EVOK est partenaire avec Hitachi Data Systems et met en place des solutions de stockage SAN et NAS haute disponibilité.</div><a id="link-17-27" class="ct-link oxel_icon_button__container" href="/company/#partners" target="_self"   role="button"><div id="fancy_icon-18-27" class="ct-fancy-icon oxel_icon_button_icon" ><svg id="svg-fancy_icon-18-27"><use xlink:href="#FontAwesomeicon-eye"></use></svg></div><div id="text_block-19-27" class="ct-text-block oxel_icon_button_text" >Nos partenaires stratégiques</div></a></div></div></div></div></li></ul></div></div><script class="ct-slider-script">jQuery(document).ready(function($){$('#slider-105-27.ct_unique_slider_7531 .oxygen-unslider-container:not(.unslider-horizontal,.unslider-fade)').unslider({autoplay: false, delay: 3000, animation: 'horizontal', speed : 750, arrows: false, nav: false, infinite: false})});</script><section id="section-186-27" class="ct-section" ><div class="ct-section-inner-wrap"><div id="new_columns-187-27" class="ct-new-columns" ><div id="div_block-205-27" class="ct-div-block" ><h2 id="headline-206-27" class="ct-headline atomic-secondary-heading">Notre expertise</h2><h2 id="headline-212-27" class="ct-headline atomic-secondary-heading">En action</h2><div id="div_block-214-27" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="text_block-216-27" class="ct-text-block" >1998 : FONDATION DE LA SOCIéTé</div><div id="text_block-218-27" class="ct-text-block" >Spécialiste en services d'infogérance, infrastructure, fournisseurs de solution cloud privées, sécurité et maintenance informatique depuis 1998, EVOK accompagne le développement des entreprises en leur proposant des solutions informatiques adaptées à leur taille et organisation.</div><div id="text_block-606-1317" class="ct-text-block" >2024 : intégration dans le groupe Sequotech<br></div><div id="text_block-610-1317" class="ct-text-block" >En 2024, EVOK a rejoint le groupe suisse Sequotech, qui compte près de 270 collaborateurs, et qui se positionne comme un acteur majeur pour les solutions IT, infrastructure, Cloud, consulting, infogérance et sécurité.&nbsp;&nbsp;</div></div><div id="div_block-221-27" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="text_block-222-27" class="ct-text-block" >3 DATACENTERS</div><div id="text_block-223-27" class="ct-text-block" >Datacenters Tier III+ et Tier IV conçus dans l’optique Green IT 100% courant vert et certifié ISO 14064 Climatisation redondante et refroidissement par Free Cooling</div></div></div><div id="div_block-188-27" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="div_block-189-27" class="ct-div-block atomic-iconblock-11-wrapper" ><img  id="image-226-27" alt="" src="https://evok.com/media/icn.svg.png" class="ct-image"/><h4 id="headline-191-27" class="ct-headline atomic-iconblock-11-title">99.99%</h4><div id="text_block-192-27" class="ct-text-block atomic-iconblock-11-text" >Datacenter Availability</div><div id="div_block-229-27" class="ct-div-block oxel_horizontal_divider" ><div id="code_block-230-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div><div id="code_block-232-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div></div></div><div id="div_block-241-27" class="ct-div-block atomic-iconblock-11-wrapper" ><img  id="image-242-27" alt="" src="https://evok.com/media/icn-1.svg.png" class="ct-image"/><h4 id="headline-243-27" class="ct-headline atomic-iconblock-11-title">5500+</h4><div id="text_block-244-27" class="ct-text-block atomic-iconblock-11-text" >Utilisateurs sous gestion</div><div id="div_block-245-27" class="ct-div-block oxel_horizontal_divider" ><div id="code_block-246-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div><div id="code_block-247-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div></div></div><div id="div_block-248-27" class="ct-div-block atomic-iconblock-11-wrapper" ><img  id="image-249-27" alt="" src="https://evok.com/media/Group-4859.svg.png" class="ct-image"/><h4 id="headline-250-27" class="ct-headline atomic-iconblock-11-title">250+</h4><div id="text_block-251-27" class="ct-text-block atomic-iconblock-11-text" >Entreprises clientes</div><div id="div_block-252-27" class="ct-div-block oxel_horizontal_divider" ><div id="code_block-253-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div><div id="code_block-254-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div></div></div><div id="div_block-234-27" class="ct-div-block atomic-iconblock-11-wrapper" ><img  id="image-235-27" alt="" src="https://evok.com/media/Group-4860.svg.png" class="ct-image"/><h4 id="headline-236-27" class="ct-headline atomic-iconblock-11-title">100%</h4><div id="text_block-237-27" class="ct-text-block atomic-iconblock-11-text" >Prestations realisees en interne</div><div id="div_block-238-27" class="ct-div-block oxel_horizontal_divider" ><div id="code_block-239-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div><div id="code_block-240-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-261-27" class="ct-section" ><div class="ct-section-inner-wrap"><div id="new_columns-262-27" class="ct-new-columns" ><div id="div_block-267-27" class="ct-div-block atomic-iconblock-11-wrapper block-line" ><img  id="image-268-27" alt="" src="https://evok.com/media/icn-2.svg.png" class="ct-image"/><h4 id="headline-269-27" class="ct-headline atomic-iconblock-11-title">40+</h4><div id="text_block-270-27" class="ct-text-block atomic-iconblock-11-text" >Collaborateurs</div><div id="div_block-271-27" class="ct-div-block oxel_horizontal_divider" ><div id="code_block-272-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div><div id="code_block-273-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div></div></div><div id="div_block-337-27" class="ct-div-block atomic-iconblock-11-wrapper block-line" ><img  id="image-338-27" alt="" src="https://evok.com/media/icn-3.svg.png" class="ct-image"/><div id="div_block-383-27" class="ct-div-block" ><h4 id="headline-382-27" class="ct-headline atomic-iconblock-11-title">25</h4><h4 id="headline-339-27" class="ct-headline"></h4></div><div id="text_block-340-27" class="ct-text-block atomic-iconblock-11-text" >Ans d'experience</div><div id="div_block-341-27" class="ct-div-block oxel_horizontal_divider" ><div id="code_block-342-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div><div id="code_block-343-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div></div></div><div id="div_block-351-27" class="ct-div-block atomic-iconblock-11-wrapper block-line" ><img  id="image-352-27" alt="" src="https://evok.com/media/icn-5.svg.png" class="ct-image"/><h4 id="headline-353-27" class="ct-headline atomic-iconblock-11-title">25+</h4><div id="text_block-354-27" class="ct-text-block atomic-iconblock-11-text" >Partenaires commerciaux<br></div><div id="div_block-355-27" class="ct-div-block oxel_horizontal_divider" ><div id="code_block-356-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div><div id="code_block-357-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div></div></div><div id="div_block-358-27" class="ct-div-block atomic-iconblock-11-wrapper block-line" ><img  id="image-359-27" alt="" src="https://evok.com/media/icn-6.svg.png" class="ct-image"/><h4 id="headline-360-27" class="ct-headline atomic-iconblock-11-title">100%</h4><div id="text_block-361-27" class="ct-text-block atomic-iconblock-11-text" >Des données&nbsp; stockées en Suisse</div><div id="div_block-362-27" class="ct-div-block oxel_horizontal_divider" ><div id="code_block-363-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div><div id="code_block-364-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div></div></div><div id="div_block-365-27" class="ct-div-block atomic-iconblock-11-wrapper block-line" ><img  id="image-366-27" alt="" src="https://evok.com/media/icn-7.svg.png" class="ct-image"/><h4 id="headline-367-27" class="ct-headline atomic-iconblock-11-title">3</h4><div id="text_block-368-27" class="ct-text-block atomic-iconblock-11-text" >Succursales en Suisse Romande</div><div id="div_block-369-27" class="ct-div-block oxel_horizontal_divider" ><div id="code_block-370-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div><div id="code_block-371-27" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div></div></div><div id="div_block-598-1317" class="ct-div-block atomic-iconblock-11-wrapper block-line" ><img  id="image-599-1317" alt="ISO 27001 certification" src="https://evok.com/media/27001_gm_fr-300x300.jpg" class="ct-image" srcset="https://evok.com/media/27001_gm_fr-300x300.jpg 300w,   https://evok.com/media/27001_gm_fr-150x150.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /><h4 id="headline-600-1317" class="ct-headline atomic-iconblock-11-title">ISO</h4><div id="text_block-601-1317" class="ct-text-block atomic-iconblock-11-text" >Certifié&nbsp;<br>ISO/IEC 27001:2022<br></div><div id="div_block-602-1317" class="ct-div-block oxel_horizontal_divider" ><div id="code_block-603-1317" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div><div id="code_block-604-1317" class="ct-code-block oxel_horizontal_divider__line" ><!-- --></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-400-27" class="ct-section" ><div class="ct-section-inner-wrap"><div id="new_columns-401-27" class="ct-new-columns" ><div id="div_block-403-27" class="ct-div-block" ></div><div id="div_block-404-27" class="ct-div-block" ><h2 id="headline-406-27" class="ct-headline">DATACENTERS SÉCURISÉS BASÉS EN SUISSE</h2><div id="text_block-407-27" class="ct-text-block" >EVOK opère ses services en Suisse, avec 3 Datacenters à 70 km, dans un environnement totalement sécurisé permettant à EVOK de fournir des garanties complètes lors de l’hébergement d’applications critiques.</div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-416-27" class="ct-section" ><div class="ct-section-inner-wrap"><div id="new_columns-417-27" class="ct-new-columns" ><div id="div_block-518-27" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="div_block-519-27" class="ct-div-block atomic-iconblock-15-wrapper" ><img  id="image-452-27" alt="" src="https://evok.com/media/icn-8.svg.png" class="ct-image"/><div id="text_block-453-27" class="ct-text-block" >24h/24 Monitoring</div></div></div><div id="div_block-550-27" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="div_block-551-27" class="ct-div-block atomic-iconblock-15-wrapper" ><img  id="image-459-27" alt="" src="https://evok.com/media/icn-12.svg.png" class="ct-image"/><div id="text_block-460-27" class="ct-text-block" >Datacenters sécurisés en Suisse</div></div></div><div id="div_block-553-27" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="div_block-554-27" class="ct-div-block atomic-iconblock-15-wrapper" ><img  id="image-462-27" alt="" src="https://evok.com/media/icn-9.svg.png" class="ct-image"/><div id="text_block-463-27" class="ct-text-block" >Infrastructure virtualisée VMware ESX</div></div></div><div id="div_block-556-27" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="div_block-557-27" class="ct-div-block atomic-iconblock-15-wrapper" ><img  id="image-465-27" alt="" src="https://evok.com/media/icn-10.svg.png" class="ct-image"/><div id="text_block-466-27" class="ct-text-block" >99,99% de disponibilité</div></div></div><div id="div_block-559-27" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="div_block-560-27" class="ct-div-block atomic-iconblock-15-wrapper" ><img  id="image-468-27" alt="" src="https://evok.com/media/icn-11.svg.png" class="ct-image"/><div id="text_block-469-27" class="ct-text-block" >Stockage SAN Hitachi</div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-474-27" class="ct-section" ><div class="ct-section-inner-wrap"><div id="new_columns-478-27" class="ct-new-columns" ><div id="div_block-479-27" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="text_block-485-27" class="ct-text-block" >N’hésitez pas à nous contacter pour un rendez-vous&nbsp;<br>ou une offre personnalisée</div><a id="link-490-27" class="ct-link oxel_icon_button__container" href="/contact-us" target="_blank"   role="button"><div id="fancy_icon-491-27" class="ct-fancy-icon oxel_icon_button_icon" ><svg id="svg-fancy_icon-491-27"><use xlink:href="#FontAwesomeicon-comments"></use></svg></div><div id="text_block-492-27" class="ct-text-block oxel_icon_button_text" >Contactez-nous</div></a></div></div></div></section><div id="code_block-597-27" class="ct-code-block" ><!-- --></div></div><section id="section-38-11" class="ct-section" ><div class="ct-section-inner-wrap"><div id="new_columns-39-11" class="ct-new-columns" ><div id="div_block-40-11" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="div_block-169-11" class="ct-div-block" ><h3 id="headline-66-11" class="ct-headline">EVOK Fribourg</h3><div id="div_block-80-11" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="fancy_icon-84-11" class="ct-fancy-icon" ><svg id="svg-fancy_icon-84-11"><use xlink:href="#FontAwesomeicon-map-marker"></use></svg></div><div id="text_block-47-11" class="ct-text-block onepage-contact-4-text" >Siège principal - Altern8 SA<br>Rte des Daillettes 21<br>1700 Fribourg<br>Suisse</div></div><div id="div_block